quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,146,"Those whom We gave them The Book they know it, as they know their sons, and that a group from them hide/conceal (E) the truth and they are knowing"
  2,147,"The truth (is) from your Lord, so do not be (E) from the doubting/arguing"
  2,148,"And for each a direction/front , he is turning towards it , so race/surpass each other (to) the goodnesses wherever you are, God comes with you altogether , that God (is) on every thing powerful/capable"
  2,149,"And from where you got out so turn your face towards the Mosque the Forbidden/Sacred , and that it is the truth (E) from your Lord, and that God (is) not with ignoring/disregarding about what you are making/doing"
  2,150,"And from where you got out , so turn your face towards the Mosque the Forbidden/Sacred , and wherever you were, so turn your faces towards it, for that the people do not (have) on you aproof/argument except those who were unjust/oppressive from them. So do not fear them and fear Me .And to complete/ perfect My blessings on you, and maybe you (will) be guided"
  2,151,"As We sent in you a messenger from you, he reads/recites on you Our verses/evidences and he purifies you and he teaches you The Book and the wisdom, and he teaches you what you were not knowing"
  2,152,"So mention/remember Me , I remember you , and thank/be grateful to Me and do not disbelieve"
  2,153,"You, you those who believed, seek help with the patience and the prayers that God (is) with the patient/enduring"